sentence.text: However, the prognostic value of gamma-aminobutyric acid catabolic process in ovarian cancer remains unclear.
The aim of this study was to explore the relationship between gamma-aminobutyric acid catabolic process and the prognosis of patients with ovarian cancer (OC).

In survival analyses, we found that gamma-aminobutyric acid catabolic process was positively linked to prognosis in patients with OC, particularly in those with serous ovarian cancer (proteasome-mediated ubiquitin-dependent protein catabolic process).
